Feature: Collissions and Directions
    Creatures can collide and
    we can find opposite directions.

    Scenario: Collide
        Given The creature is at (60, 60)
        When The player is at (60, 60)
        Then A collision has occurred

    Scenario: Miss
        Given The creature is at (60, 60)
        When The player is at (50, 50)
        Then A collision has not occurred
